In[]:
import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

data=pd.read_csv('./Warehouse - Warehouse.csv')

Histogram

In[]:
plt.hist(data["PERFORMANCE"],bins=10,color="green",alpha=1.0)
plt.title('Histogram')
plt.xlabel('Performance')
plt.ylabel('Frequency')
plt.show()

Scatter Plot

In[]:
plt.scatter(data["COUNTRY_ID"],data["LIST_PRICE"])

plt.xlabel('Country')
plt.ylabel('List Price')
plt.title('Scatterplot')

plt.show()

Line Plot

In[]:
data = data.sort_values(by='PERFORMANCE')

plt.plot(data["PERFORMANCE"], data["RATING"], marker='o', linestyle='-')

plt.xlabel('Performance')
plt.ylabel('Rating')
plt.title('Line Plot')

plt.show()

Bar Graph

In[]:
category_totals = data['LIST_PRICE'].value_counts()
category_totals.plot(kind='bar',color='green')

plt.xlabel('List Price')
plt.ylabel('Count')
plt.title('Bar graph')

plt.show()

Pie Chart

In[]:
data_grouped = data.groupby(["PERFORMANCE", "RATING"]).size().reset_index(name='count')

plt.pie(data_grouped['count'], labels=data_grouped['PERFORMANCE'] + '-' + data_grouped['RATING'], autopct='%1.1f%%')

plt.title('Pie Chart')

plt.axis('equal')  
plt.show()

Area plot

In[]:
data.set_index('PERFORMANCE').count().cumsum().plot(kind='area')
plt.xlabel("Performance")
plt.ylabel("Cumulative frequency")
plt.title("Area Plot")
plt.show()

Box plot

In[]:
data.plot.box()
plt.title("BoxPlot")
plt.xticks(fontsize=8)
plt.show()

Pair plot
